<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #1f2937; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 20px; color: #4f46e5; }
    ul { line-height: 1.8; }
    p { line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>A Slot Has Opened for You</h1>
  <p>Good news! A slot has become available for a service you are waitlisted for:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Business:</strong> {{businessName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Service:</strong> {{serviceName}}</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Open the Qulene app to book your appointment before the slot is taken.</p>
  <p class="footer">Qulene &mdash; Waitlist &amp; Appointment Manager</p>
</body>
</html>
